{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x31,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* The view of the sunset from here hasn't changed a bit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ever since then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Mr. Harry, are you out for a walk?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, hmhm, a walk? Well I guess it's something like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "When things don't go well at work,<CR>I always come here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "This is a great view. It's like my feelings are getting refreshed, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I've challenged you at every Thrilling Treasure Contest, but I've lost every battle..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I came here because I wanted to reflect back on myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It's a familiar view that I've seen for many years. And now, I suddenly remember something about my past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'll be reminiscing, but would you mind listening to my story?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "An old story about you? If it's okay with you, I'd love to hear it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Thank you. It's been 30 years since then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Before you were born, this town wasn't as big as it is today, and I was but a child."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "We had years of bad harvests back then, and there were many years where people didn't have enough to eat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "My family has been trading for<CR>generations, so we were somewhat<CR>well-off, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Even still, there were many times when we had trouble getting food."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "There was a time like that...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Even so, my mother somehow devised a way to make me snacks."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Back then, you couldn't eat till you were full, so she probably wanted to at least give me a little taste."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, mothers are always so strong, I guess."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, time passed and I became an adult, and the food supply had gotten better..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "And at the very least, I don't suffer from starvation anymore. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I still can't forget the taste of that snack that my mother made for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "It must've been an amazing snack,<CR>made with your mother's love."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "You're right. No treasure can match that taste."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Now, let's return to the present, for this story doesn't end in the past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Currently, I have lost my former glory and I am at the depths of disappointment."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Losing to you, my heart has been wounded, and I'm looking at the same sunset as before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "My title as the Collector King has become a thing of the past... In the very same past as my mother's snack."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't know about the latter, but I don't think the first part is true..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to cheer me up. So basically, I'm very depressed right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "To heal this wounded heart, the snack that my mother made for me would be perfect."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "However, it's very difficult to explain what kind of taste it was, and there is no recipe for it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I was totally at a loss as to what I should do, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Then I thought, \"I know! Ayesha can do something about it!\" And so, I have been waiting for you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Uh...huhhh!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "I-It's not like homemade sweets are my forte..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "No. From what I've heard, you're able to create various things with synthesis, besides just medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "So, about my mother's snack...<CR>I thought maybe...you could..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "No, you can do it... This is something only you can do!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Please! You and I have a wonderful relationship. Please just help me by recreating that taste!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "You don't have to beg me. I'm not sure if I can do it, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "I'll give it a try..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Thank you! I knew you'd say that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x57,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "For me to recover from my disappointment, and to pursue new knowledge to the extreme..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x58,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "I need to return to my roots.<CR>This is for that very purpose."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure it won't be easy,<CR>but I'm counting on you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, I couldn't decline. What should I do? I wonder what kind of taste he's talking about...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "(Maybe Mr. Fred will know something about this? I should go ask him.)"
        }
    ]
}